{"tid":1560401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[流水革命之球場愛港00後] 中學生不夠錢買飛，堅持在場外打氣","createTime":"2019-09-11T07:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T07:44:56.000Z","uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"67544a5d374796f8303c8d654cf24695ab5cbdff","tid":1560401,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:35:58.000Z","msg":"10/9　香港大球場<br />\n<br />\n中學生不夠錢買飛，堅持在場外打氣<br />\n<br />\n＊　＊　＊<br />\n<br />\n當香港對伊朗的賽事已經開始，三名中學生怔怔地站在場外。筆者提醒他們還可即場買飛，但他們很快頹然而返 － 特價的學生飛早已售罄，180 蚊的正價飛他們買不起。<br />\n<br />\n連阮囊羞澀的筆者也感於心不忍掏出銀包，告訴他們來日可捐同額的錢給慈善機構，毋須介懷。然而三位學生堅拒：「我地唔可以收錢。」<br />\n<br />\n從對答可知三人非資深球迷，筆者問他們幹嘛。女生露出慧黠的笑容，「你一早就知。」筆者轉問他們是否背好歌辭，他們立即點頭。<br />\n<br />\n偶爾場內傳出《無盡》的歌聲，他們便興奮地在場外揮手機和應。<br />\n<br />\n結果三人在場外守候逾一小時，等到球賽完結，球迷蜂擁而出，他們終於得償心願，走入人群之中，和民眾一起唱《願榮光歸香港》。<br />\n<br />\n他們苦心孤詣，就是為了這一刻而來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n沒有暴徒，只有暴政<br />\n願榮光歸香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"1e2b0c3c102886c574ef8b6b0e603e3ed50404ef","tid":1560401,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H4Nr6Ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH4Nr6Ad.jpg&h=67271e00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21f943a7606eb7606973896592613b304c1cf462","tid":1560401,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GiW8u64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiW8u64.jpg&h=6e2a8a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"2542a79d942e467b0c4fa767ebab3a84f295ee62","tid":1560401,"uid":260570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:38:54.000Z","msg":"diu好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee37634ba3f25d3e94cab3e328f80836d39404d8","tid":1560401,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bTMDXKC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbTMDXKC.jpg&h=6875e0a0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}